Author: mattmaroon
Content: I think driverless cars need to be supported and mandated by government. It's far easier and safer to make cars that drive themselves when the roads are designed for that purpose and all other cars as well. Making a car that can drive on our current roads and dodge blind old ladies is a far harder problem.
